message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product at a great value, and I believe it will fit your needs well. I'm willing to sell it to you for $12000.

Hi Alice, thank you for your offer. However, the price is a bit higher than I'm willing to pay. I'd like to make a counteroffer of $8000. I believe this is a fair price, and I'm willing to make a deal if you're willing to meet me at this price.
